quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  14,11,"Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen jaabori …ìe: Ko goonga, men wonaali si wanaa …ìanndinke yeru mon. Ko woni tun, …óum hollaa hi…óen nannda e kala huunde. Alla no hertinira neeminirgol on Mo O muuyi e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, O su…ìoo e ma…ì…ìe Nulaa…ìe e yim…ìe …ìen. Menen, haananaa men nde men addanta on hujja mo …óa…ì…ìoton, si wanaa e du≈ãayee Alla, men hattanaaka addugol …óum, ko Alla tun woni hattan…óo e …óum. Ko e Alla tun woni ko gom…óim…ìe …ìe Mo …ìen fawatoo e fiyakuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin fow."
  14,12,"Ko ha…óata men haa men he…ìa ngantu, wonoowo hakkunde e amen e fawagol Mo ngol? Gom…óii le O fewnirii men e laawol …ìurngol foccaade …ìannga. Pellet men mu√±√±otoo e kon ko lorroton men e fennugol jalkita. Ko e Alla tun woni ko gom…óim…ìe …ìen fawatoo e denndaangal fiyakuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin."
  14,13,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen e yim…ìe Nulaa…ìe …ìen wi'i tuma …ìe ronkunoo wenjondirgol e Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen: Ma men yaltin on e saare amen, maa on yiltike e diina mon faade e diina amen. Alla wahayiniri e Nulaa…ìe …ìen √±innugol …ìe: Ma men halku too√±u…ìe yeddi Alla e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  14,14,"Ma Men ho…ónu on, onon Nulaa…ìe …ìen e jokku…ìe on, e leydi ndin, …ìaawo nde …ìe halkaa. Kon ko jantaa e halkugol heefer…ìe fennoo…ìe …ìen, ho…óina Nulaa…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe …ìen ka leydi …ìaawo halkeede …ìeya, …óum ko anndu…óo mawngu Am e ndeena Am e makko, o huli ko Mi kammbiranta mo lepte kon."
  14,15,"Nulaa…ìe …ìen …óa…ì…ìiri Joomi ma…ì…ìe walleede e ay…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen. Ontuma sooyi kala dunndaranke ∆¥aggango goonga, salotoo…óo jokkude goonga si fee√±anii mo."
  14,16,"√ëalnde Darngal, on dunndarankeejo tawoyay Jahannama yesso makko, ka o waawataa laawaade. O yarniroyee e magge mbordi yim…ìe Yiite ndin ilayndi e ma…ì…ìe. ∆äum …óon…óitataa mo, o seerataa himo leptiree …óonka e kala noone e lepte."
  14,17,"Himo etoo yarugol …óam ndiyam tuma kala, kono o e…ì…ìataa mo…óugol …óam hakkee ko …óam metti …óam wuli luu…ìi. Maayde nden no ardana mo kala nokku, hakkee ko lepte …óen sattiri mo, kono le o maayataa sakko o fowtoo. Ko e …óum o heddotoo himo mee…óa lepte. Hara kadi lepte sattu…óe goo no habbitii mo yeeso."
  14,18,"Ko woni sifa golle …óe yeddu…ìe …ìen gollata immorde e sadaka, e mo∆¥∆¥ere, e yurmegol lo'u…ìe, ko wano ndoondi ndi henndu tii…ói e mun, e √±alaande wippo- re; ndun henndu ronndora ndi ndoondi ndi henndu wutti e mbaadi sattundi, ndu saakita e kala nokku, haa batte mayri mula. Ko non golle heefer- …ìe …ìen wa'i, ko keeferaaku ngun wippotoo…óe, …ìe nafitoroytaa …óe √ëalnde Darngal. ∆äen woni golle …óe tuuginaaki e gom…óinal, ko …óen woni majjere wo…ó…óunde laawol goonga ngol."